WEBVTT

00:01.735 --> 00:03.069
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.069 --> 00:04.337
IF HIS MOTHER IS NOT HERE
BY TOMORROW,

00:04.337 --> 00:05.706
HE WILL BE PLACED
IN FOSTER CARE.

00:05.706 --> 00:08.108
YOU WILL BE AT MY HOUSE
FOR DINNER,

00:08.108 --> 00:10.711
OR THE POLICE WILL BE
AT CANDACE'S HOUSE

00:10.711 --> 00:11.912
WITH A SEARCH WARRANT.

00:11.912 --> 00:14.347
I THINK YOU MEET
JUDGE DAVID HARRINGTON.

00:14.347 --> 00:16.550
YOU WANT ME TO TURN BACK ON THE
PHONES OVER AT BENNY'S TOWING?

00:16.550 --> 00:18.985
THAT PUNK
IS THREATENING MY SON.

00:18.985 --> 00:20.587
STAY THE HELL AWAY
FROM MY SON.

00:20.587 --> 00:22.388
HEY, MAN, YOU HEAR ME?

00:25.892 --> 00:27.360
[ GUNSHOT ]

00:27.360 --> 00:28.929
AAH!

00:30.597 --> 00:32.599
♪♪♪♪

00:38.805 --> 00:42.242
BENNY, STOP!
GET OFF, GET OFF! RIGHT NOW!

00:42.242 --> 00:44.444
THE FOOL TRIED TO KILL ME!
BACK IT OFF! BACK IT OFF!

00:44.444 --> 00:45.979
HE TRIED TO KILL ME, MAN.

00:45.979 --> 00:47.748
HE TRIED TO KILL ME.
FOOL TRIED TO KILL ME.

00:47.748 --> 00:49.816
HOW DARE YOU ASSAULT A JUDGE!

00:49.816 --> 00:51.217
YOU DON'T SCARE ME,
SON OF A BITCH.

00:51.217 --> 00:52.819
GET OUT OF HERE.
MAKE ME. COME ON.

00:52.819 --> 00:55.055
I'LL MAKE YOU, ALL RIGHT. HUH?
COME WITH IT, COME WITH IT.

00:55.055 --> 00:56.389
OH, WHAT,
YOU SCARED, HUH?

00:56.389 --> 00:57.958
YOU SCARED
'CAUSE A WHITE BOY SAW THIS?

00:57.958 --> 00:59.159
THAT'S WHAT IT IS.
YOU SCARED, HUH?

00:59.159 --> 01:00.961
OH, WHAT? YOU'RE A CHILD.
YOU ARE A CHILD.

01:00.961 --> 01:02.669
YEAH, "CHILD."
I GOT YOUR CHILD RIGHT HERE.

01:02.669 --> 01:04.437
OH, SHUT UP.
YOU GO TO HELL, MAN.

01:04.437 --> 01:06.006
YOU ALREADY ON YOUR WAY THERE.
OH, YOU DON'T SCARE ME.

01:06.006 --> 01:08.174
GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE.
COME ON, MAKE ME.

01:08.174 --> 01:10.043
OH, I'LL MAKE YOU, ALL RIGHT.
I'LL MAKE YOU.

01:10.043 --> 01:11.712
COME ON.
WHAT? YOU MAD?

01:11.712 --> 01:13.446
HUH? YOU MAD
'CAUSE YOUR WIFE WANTS ALL THIS?

01:13.446 --> 01:15.015
THAT'S WHAT IT IS.
YOU MAD?

01:15.015 --> 01:16.316
YOU'RE A CHILD.
A CHILD?

01:16.316 --> 01:17.651
I GOT YOUR CHILD
RIGHT HERE, BITCH.

01:17.651 --> 01:19.786
THAT'S A CHILDISH BEHAVIOR.
CHILDISH BEHAVIOR!

01:19.786 --> 01:21.087
YOU WIFE LIKES
THIS CHILDISH BEHAVIOR.

01:21.087 --> 01:22.455
BACK IT OFF!

01:22.455 --> 01:23.790
WHY DON'T YOU
SHUT YOUR BITCH ASS UP?

01:23.790 --> 01:25.225
YOU BETTER GET
MY DAMN PHONES ON.

01:25.225 --> 01:26.593
THE PHONES IS THE LEAST
OF YOUR TROUBLES.

01:26.593 --> 01:27.694
[ SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY ]

01:27.694 --> 01:28.795
COME ON.
KNOCK IT OFF!

01:28.795 --> 01:30.564
STAY BACK.
TO HELL WITH HIM.

01:30.564 --> 01:31.732
STAY BACK.
YEAH.

01:31.732 --> 01:34.234
GIVE ME THAT.
HERE YOU GO. STAY BACK.

01:34.234 --> 01:36.503
YOU REMEMBER THE CAR
AND THE COCAINE?

01:36.503 --> 01:37.771
WHAT?!

01:37.771 --> 01:39.973
YOU HEARD ME.
WHAT YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT, MAN?

01:39.973 --> 01:42.943
I KNOW ALL ABOUT THAT.
YOU THINK THAT WAS SOMETHING?

01:42.943 --> 01:45.111
YEAH, WELL, YOUR WIFE
GOT ME OFF THEN,

01:45.111 --> 01:47.147
KIND OF LIKE SHE'LL BE
GETTING ME OFF AFTER THAT, YEAH.

01:47.147 --> 01:49.115
NO, NO, SHE WASN'T THE ONE
THAT GOT YOU OFF.

01:49.115 --> 01:51.117
KNOCK IT OFF, ALL RIGHT?
I GOT HIS ASS.

01:51.117 --> 01:52.619
NO, GET INSIDE.
TO HELL WITH YOU, MAN.

01:52.619 --> 01:53.820
GET INSIDE. I GOT THIS, MAN.
WHY?

01:53.820 --> 01:55.756
I GOT IT! GO.

01:55.756 --> 01:58.358
YOU'RE LUCKY, MAN.
DON'T TOUCH ME!

01:58.358 --> 01:59.926
GET INSIDE!
YOU'RE LUCKY.

01:59.926 --> 02:00.967
I GOT THIS.
I'M GONNA KILL YOU!

02:00.967 --> 02:03.036
GET IN THERE.
STAY IN THERE.

