THE POLICE.

29:31.932 --> 29:33.133
WHAT?

29:33.133 --> 29:37.604
WELL, MS. YOUNG
FALSIFIED SOME DOCUMENTS.

29:37.604 --> 29:38.839
SHE DID?

29:38.839 --> 29:40.040
YEP.

29:40.040 --> 29:41.642
HER BROTHER'S NAME
IS ON THE DEED,

29:41.642 --> 29:44.377
BUT AS YOU CAN SEE,

29:44.377 --> 29:47.548
THE SIGNATURES
DON'T MATCH.

29:47.548 --> 29:49.950
IS THAT SO?

