MS. YOUNG ON THE PHONE.

30:01.935 --> 30:03.369
I WANT YOU TO TELL HER
TO GET HER SWEET ASS

30:03.369 --> 30:05.939
DOWN TO THE BANK
IN 24 HOURS

30:05.939 --> 30:09.142
AND RETURN
ALL OF THE MONEY.

30:09.142 --> 30:12.245
OR YOU WILL CALL THE POLICE.

30:12.245 --> 30:14.247
YOU'LL HAVE TO HAVE
HER ARRESTED,

30:14.247 --> 30:16.382
AND ALL OF HER PROPERTIES
WILL BE FORECLOSED ON

30:16.382 --> 30:18.852
BECAUSE
OF THE FALSIFIED DOCUMENT.

30:18.852 --> 30:21.421
[ CHUCKLES ]
ARE YOU SURE?

30:21.421 --> 30:22.656
LOOK AT THIS FACE.

30:22.656 --> 30:25.959
DO I LOOK LIKE I'M KIDDING?

30:25.959 --> 30:28.428
OKAY.

30:28.428 --> 30:31.097
YOU PROMISE ME
THERE IS NO WAY IN HELL

30:31.097 --> 30:33.567
THAT SHE STILL
HAS THIS MONEY?

30:33.567 --> 30:34.601
UNLESS SHE CAME DOWN HERE

30:34.601 --> 30:36.202
AND GOT IT
FROM THE EVIDENCE ROOM,

30:36.202 --> 30:38.739
SHE DOESN'T HAVE IT.

30:38.739 --> 30:40.040
ALL RIGHT,
THEN YOU DO THIS THING.

30:40.040 --> 30:41.908
YOU START NOW.
OKAY.

30:41.908 --> 30:44.077
NOW.
GO ON, START.

30:52.318 --> 30:54.487
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

31:03.604 --> 31:05.271
