HI.

31:05.271 --> 31:07.974
COME IN.

31:07.974 --> 31:10.243
YOU DON'T LOOK SO GOOD.

31:10.243 --> 31:12.946
I'M JUST TIRED.
OH.

31:12.946 --> 31:14.515
THIS WON'T TAKE LONG,
I PROMISE.

31:14.515 --> 31:15.516
