31:30.664 --> 31:32.432
NOT THIS AGAIN.

31:32.432 --> 31:35.435
I JUST WANT YOU
TO READ THIS.

31:35.435 --> 31:36.703
WHAT?

31:36.703 --> 31:38.605
JUST ‐‐
JUST THIS PARAGRAPH.

31:41.274 --> 31:43.109
ARE YOU DYING,
AND I DON'T KNOW IT?

31:43.109 --> 31:44.811
