31:44.811 --> 31:45.846
HANNA.

31:45.846 --> 31:49.282
IS IT CANCER?

31:49.282 --> 31:51.752
NO, I'M FINE.

31:51.752 --> 31:54.087
THEN...

31:54.087 --> 31:55.522
WHA‐‐ WHAT?

31:55.522 --> 31:57.123
WHY?

31:59.993 --> 32:02.368
WE SHOULD ALL BE PREPARED.

32:02.368 --> 32:04.270
SHOULD WE?

32:04.270 --> 32:05.338
WELL, DON'T YOU HAVE
A WILL?

32:05.338 --> 32:07.207
NO.
HANNA, YOU NEED A WILL.

32:07.207 --> 32:09.810
I DON'T HAVE
ANYTHING TO WILL.

32:09.810 --> 32:11.745
WELL, YOU'LL NEED ONE
AFTER YOU READ THIS.

32:11.745 --> 32:13.379
WHAT?

32:13.379 --> 32:15.916
READ IT.

32:23.990 --> 32:26.226
YOU'RE LEAVING ME
$5 MILLION?!

32:29.329 --> 32:31.297
YES.

32:31.297 --> 32:33.667
MRS. CRYER.

32:33.667 --> 32:37.738
AND DON'T TELL ME
YOU DON'T ACCEPT THAT.

32:37.738 --> 32:40.340
I DON'T.

32:40.340 --> 32:44.545
HANNA, NO ONE IN MY LIFE

32:44.545 --> 32:48.549
HAS BEEN THE KIND OF ROCK
THAT YOU HAVE BEEN FOR ME.

32:48.549 --> 32:50.584
YOU WILL ACCEPT THIS.

32:53.319 --> 32:57.290
THANK YOU.

32:57.290 --> 33:00.060
YOU'RE WELCOME.

33:00.060 --> 33:03.737
I HOPE YOU OUTLIVE ME.

33:03.737 --> 33:05.606
I WON'T.

33:05.606 --> 33:09.543
WHY DO YOU SAY THAT?

33:09.543 --> 33:12.646
HAVE YOU SEEN THE DRAMA
AND STRESS IN MY LIFE?

33:12.646 --> 33:16.517
HAVE YOU SEEN THE DRAMA
AND STRESS IN MINE?

33:16.517 --> 33:20.987
BUT YOU PRAY
AND KEEP MOVING ON.

33:20.987 --> 33:22.355
I TRY TO.

33:25.391 --> 33:27.928
THANK YOU.

33:30.196 --> 33:32.833
YOU'RE WELCOME.

33:32.833 --> 33:34.801
THAT'S ALL RIGHT.
THANK YOU.

33:36.903 --> 33:38.271
I THINK THIS IS
THE KINDEST THING

33:38.271 --> 33:41.474
ANYBODY'S EVER DONE FOR ME.

33:41.474 --> 33:44.711
WELL, PEOPLE
SHOULD DO MORE FOR YOU.

33:44.711 --> 33:46.246
THANK YOU.

33:48.782 --> 33:50.250
