ONE OF THOSE THINGS

33:50.250 --> 33:53.987
THAT I HOPE IT TAKES
A LONG TIME TO GET.

33:57.624 --> 33:59.860
WELL, ME TOO.

34:03.804 --> 34:05.639
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

34:05.639 --> 34:07.608
