YOU HAVE A BUSY DAY.

34:07.608 --> 34:10.476
YEAH, I DO.

34:10.476 --> 34:12.713
ARE YOU
GOING TO SEE WYATT?

34:15.982 --> 34:18.819
I WAS GONNA BE
AT THE HOSPITAL.

34:18.819 --> 34:20.887
I'D LIKE YOU
TO SEE HOW HE IS.

34:20.887 --> 34:22.923
OKAY.

34:22.923 --> 34:25.592
I'LL CALL YOU.

34:25.592 --> 34:28.128
THANKS.

34:32.398 --> 34:34.935
MRS. CRYER, UM...

34:36.970 --> 34:40.741
...I HAVE A FAVOR
TO ASK YOU, TOO.

34:40.741 --> 34:43.276
ANYTHING.

34:47.447 --> 34:51.752
IF I GO TO JAIL,
WOULD YOU GET ME OUT?

34:51.752 --> 34:53.887
ARE YOU PLANNING
ON COMMITTING A CRIME?

34:58.291 --> 35:00.901
YEAH.

35:00.901 --> 35:03.770
WHAT KIND?

35:03.770 --> 35:06.940
I JUST NEED YOU
TO GET ME OUT.

35:06.940 --> 35:10.711
HANNA,
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

35:10.711 --> 35:12.579
I'LL CALL YOU.

35:12.579 --> 35:13.747
HANNA, YOU TELL ME.
WHAT ‐‐

35:13.747 --> 35:15.415
NOBODY'S GONNA BE HURT.

35:15.415 --> 35:17.317
HANNA, WHAT IS GOING ON?

35:17.317 --> 35:19.085
SORRY.
HANNA.

35:19.085 --> 35:20.987
I'M SORRY.
HANNA.

35:20.987 --> 35:22.589
HANNA, WAIT.

35:22.589 --> 35:24.825
WHAT'S ‐‐ HANNA!

35:34.100 --> 35:36.503
♪♪♪♪

35:36.503 --> 35:37.704
[ KNOCKING ]

35:39.706 --> 35:42.108
JEFFERY.
HEY.

35:42.108 --> 35:44.410
HEY.
[ SIGHS ]

35:44.410 --> 35:45.512
JEFFERY.

35:48.615 --> 35:52.285
YOU SHOULD HAVE CALLED ME
TO TELL ME YOU WERE COMING.

35:52.285 --> 35:55.656
SORRY ABOUT THAT.

35:55.656 --> 35:57.991
YOU'VE BEEN CRYING?
[ SNIFFLES ]

35:57.991 --> 36:00.967
NO.

36:00.967 --> 36:02.736
WELL, YEAH.

36:02.736 --> 36:05.038
YEAH.

36:05.038 --> 36:07.273
YOU'VE BEEN CRYING.

36:07.273 --> 36:08.775
HAVE YOU BEEN CRYING?

36:11.277 --> 36:13.547
WYATT?

36:13.547 --> 36:17.618
YEAH, BUT HE'S OKAY.

36:17.618 --> 36:18.619
REALLY?
YEAH.

36:18.619 --> 36:20.120
HE DIDN'T DIE.

36:22.989 --> 36:24.357
WOW.

36:24.357 --> 36:27.493
HE WAS FOUND.
AND, UH, HE DID O. D., THOUGH.

36:27.493 --> 36:31.231
BUT HE'S GONNA MAKE IT.

36:31.231 --> 36:33.199
I'M SURE
THAT MAKES YOU FEEL GOOD.

36:33.199 --> 36:35.736
YEAH.

36:38.071 --> 36:40.874
SO, I MEAN,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

36:40.874 --> 36:43.810
WHAT WERE YOU
CRYING ABOUT?

36:43.810 --> 36:47.147
WHAT'S THE POINT
IN TALKING ABOUT IT?

36:47.147 --> 36:48.348
IT HELPS.

36:48.348 --> 36:51.818
DOES IT?

36:51.818 --> 36:54.688
OR IS THAT WHAT THEY
TAUGHT YOU IN SCHOOL?

36:54.688 --> 36:57.157
NO, IT HELPS.

36:59.726 --> 37:01.768
MY SON.

37:01.768 --> 37:03.670
WHAT?
WHAT ABOUT HIM?

37:03.670 --> 37:04.804
[ SIGHS ]

37:04.804 --> 37:07.674
I LOVE HIM SO MUCH.

37:07.674 --> 37:10.043
AND I'M AFRAID.

37:10.043 --> 37:13.580
WHY?

37:13.580 --> 37:15.515
I CAN'T BRING HIM HERE.

37:15.515 --> 37:16.850
MM.

37:16.850 --> 37:21.387
HIS FATHER IS DEAD
AND BURIED IN MY BACKYARD.

37:21.387 --> 37:23.289
WHAT IF HE WANTS
TO PLAY OUT THERE?

37:23.289 --> 37:25.826
HE CAN'T.

37:27.961 --> 37:29.663
I CAN'T LEAVE HIM
WITH MY MOTHER.

37:29.663 --> 37:32.599
JUST ‐‐ I CAN'T.

37:32.599 --> 37:34.100
WELL, CANDACE...

37:34.100 --> 37:35.936
NO, HE ‐‐

37:35.936 --> 37:39.305
JEFFERY, SHE'S NOT RIGHT.

37:39.305 --> 37:42.876
WELL, SHE'S BETTER
THAN MINE, FOR SURE.

37:46.046 --> 37:48.181
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

37:48.181 --> 37:50.784
I SPOKE WITH YOUR MOTHER.

37:50.784 --> 37:55.155
AND SHE WALKS IN KINDNESS.

37:55.155 --> 37:57.891
YEAH,
WITH EVERYBODY BUT ME.

37:57.891 --> 38:01.735
BUT YOU'VE DONE A LOT,
CANDACE.

38:01.735 --> 38:03.436
AND SO HAS SHE.

38:03.436 --> 38:05.405
BUT PEOPLE CHANGE.

38:05.405 --> 38:09.676
HAS YOUR MOTHER?

38:09.676 --> 38:12.178
NO.
NO, SHE HASN'T.

38:12.178 --> 38:13.847
EXACTLY.

38:13.847 --> 38:15.649
BUT THEY'RE
TWO DIFFERENT PEOPLE.

38:15.649 --> 38:18.585
MY MOTHER LIVES IN HATE.

38:18.585 --> 38:19.920
SHE CONTROLS EVERYTHING.

38:19.920 --> 38:24.525
SHE NEEDS EVERYTHING
TO LOOK PERFECT ON THE OUTSIDE.

38:24.525 --> 38:27.661
YOUR MOTHER DOESN'T CARE WHAT
THINGS LOOK LIKE ON THE OUTSIDE.

38:27.661 --> 38:31.331
SHE JUST WANTS IT
TO COME FROM A PURE PLACE.

38:31.331 --> 38:34.500
THAT CAN'T BE WRONG.

38:34.500 --> 38:37.070
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

38:37.070 --> 38:39.339
I'M GONNA GIVE MY SON UP
FOR ADOPTION.

38:42.008 --> 38:44.545
REALLY?

38:47.313 --> 38:51.051
MM‐HMM.

38:51.051 --> 38:54.788
I CAN'T LEAVE HIM
WITH MY MOTHER.

38:54.788 --> 38:58.224
I JUST ‐‐ I CAN'T.

38:58.224 --> 39:00.594
AND...

39:00.594 --> 39:02.035
I CAN'T RAISE HIM.

39:02.035 --> 39:04.738
