39:04.738 --> 39:08.609
I'M SO MESSED UP, JEFFERY.

39:08.609 --> 39:10.476
AND I'M SO BROKEN.

39:14.581 --> 39:17.684
I JUST...

39:17.684 --> 39:19.953
