TOO MANY PEOPLE.

39:22.455 --> 39:24.725
AND ONE DAY, THIS IS
ALL GONNA CATCH UP TO ME.

39:24.725 --> 39:26.426
IT'S...

39:26.426 --> 39:29.462
ACTUALLY, IT'S CATCHING UP
TO ME NOW...

39:29.462 --> 39:30.997
EVERY DAY.

39:33.700 --> 39:35.068
I CAN'T BRING HIM
INTO THIS.

39:35.068 --> 39:38.839
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S NOT RIGHT.

39:41.341 --> 39:43.176
I CAN'T.

39:43.176 --> 39:48.214
WELL, ARE YOU SURE YOU CAN'T
LEAVE HIM WITH YOUR MOTHER?

39:48.214 --> 39:51.451
WOULD YOU LEAVE YOURS
WITH YOUR MOTHER?

39:51.451 --> 39:53.720
APPARENTLY SO.

39:53.720 --> 39:56.690
SHE'S, UH,
MOVED MELISSA IN,

39:56.690 --> 40:01.367
AND I HAVE TO MOVE IN
WITH HER.

40:01.367 --> 40:03.804
JEFFERY.

40:03.804 --> 40:06.807
IF I DON'T PROPOSE
THIS EVENING,

40:06.807 --> 40:11.177
THE POLICE ARE GONNA SERVE
A WARRANT AT THIS PLACE.

40:11.177 --> 40:15.315
YOU DIDN'T PUT THE KNIFE IN
DEEP ENOUGH.

40:15.315 --> 40:18.384
I DIDN'T MEAN TO DO THAT.

40:18.384 --> 40:20.654
YOU SURE?

40:20.654 --> 40:23.123
I SNAPPED.

40:23.123 --> 40:27.127
THEN SNAP AGAIN.

40:27.127 --> 40:29.229
COME ON, CANDACE.

40:29.229 --> 40:31.898
[ SIGHS ]

40:31.898 --> 40:34.334
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

40:34.334 --> 40:35.869
I DON'T KNOW.

40:38.772 --> 40:41.608
YOU ARE THE BAD BITCH.

40:41.608 --> 40:46.012
AND YOU DO ALWAYS SEEM
TO HAVE THE ANSWERS.

40:46.012 --> 40:47.981
WELL, THIS BAD BITCH
IS TIRED.

40:50.951 --> 40:54.087
AND I'M RUNNING OUT
OF ANSWERS.

40:56.189 --> 40:58.124
AND I'M RUNNING OUT OF TIME.

41:01.434 --> 41:03.970
♪♪♪♪

41:27.460 --> 41:30.597
